{{#extend "baseLayout" title="행햟햨햟향 햡쮐쮏 햨 쒬햢햟혢햣"}}
  {{#content "body"}}
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 30px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #fff7e6; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
        
        <h2 style="color: #ff9900; font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px;">游낇 뉋썜 향햟햨햟향 햡쮐쮏 햨 쒬햢햟혢햣</h2>
        <p style="color: #333; font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
          행햟햨햟향 No{{orderNumber}} 쮏웷쟳얧썛왐 쒫썜  혞햫햨혝햣 쒬햢햟혢햦.
        </p>

        <table style="width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: #444; margin-bottom: 25px;">
          <tr>
            <td><strong>햏쮏쨿왐 향햟햨햟향햟:</strong></td>
            <td>{{orderNumber}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>혞햫햨혝 쒬햢햟혢햦:</strong></td>
            <td>{{pickupPoint.name}}, {{pickupPoint.address}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>햖햟혜혦 햟햠쮐혦:</strong></td>
            <td>{{pickupPoint.hours}}</td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #888; text-align: center;">
          쮏웷썛혞햧혜혝햟, 향햟햠햣햦혝햣 향햟햨햟향  혞햨햟향햟햫햫쮏 쒬햣햪혪 햟햠쮐혦 혞햫햨혝햟 쒬햢햟혢햦.
        </p>

      </td>
    </tr>
  {{/content}}
{{/extend}}